    },
    "Explanation": {
      "type": "string",
      "content": "<div style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;'><strong>Migration</strong> refers to the seasonal or periodic movement of organisms (e.g., birds, whales). <em>Photosynthesis</em> is energy production in plants; <em>phagocytosis</em> is cell ingestion.</div>"
